600 mr-2\"></i> Go Live in Seconds</div>\n                <h1 class=\"text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6\">Stream Like a<br/><span class=\"gradient-pink\">Pro Today</span></h1>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8\">Professional live streaming for content creators. Ultra-low latency, HD quality, engage with your audience in real-time. No equipment needed.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\">\n                    <button onclick=\"openModal()\" class=\"bg-pink-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-pink-700 transition shadow-lg\">Start Free</button>\n                    <button class=\"border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:border-pink-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition\">Watch Demo</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"hidden lg:block relative\">\n                <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-200 to-rose-200 rounded-2xl h-96 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                    <div class=\"live-pulse\"><div class=\"play-btn\"><i class=\"fas fa-play text-white text-3xl ml-2\"></i></div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-16\">Everything You Need to Stream</h2>\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-video text-pink-600\"></i></div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Ultra Low Latency</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600\">Sub-second